{"title":"脏话过滤","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":7,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2761","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>某论坛希望打造文明论坛，对于每个帖子需要将脏话换成*输出。</p>\n<p>脏话有38,250,2B，BT，TMD，PIG，SHIT，FUCK。</p>\n<p>若没有一个脏字，则此人文明。</p>\n<p>否则不文明。</p>\n<p>对于有重叠部分的脏话需全部替换。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>字符串</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>修改字符串</p>\n<p>是否文明（YES或NO）。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>322BBBTTFUCPIGKSHITMDD8</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>32**B**TFUC***K******D8</p>\n<p>NO</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>字符串长度&lt;=100.只有数字和大写字母。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}